name: "Metaphysical Observer" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Crayon, colored pencil, and felt pen on reclaimed cardboard with digital embellishments and color.] Bunny is enlightened---a bright spark in a dark universe---but such illumination often casts horrifying shadows. And in those shadows, there are sometimes beasts in waiting... ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
